<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>DT-466E and 530E Diesel Engine Service (1995 through 1999) - SECTION 7: VIBRATION DAMPER, CRANKSHAFT, MAIN
        BEARINGS, FLYWHEEL AND CRANKCASE - REAR PTO HOUSING ASSEMBLY REMOVAL (IF EQUIPPED) - REAR OIL SEAL CARRIER
        INSTALLATION
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="3">
        <title>REAR OIL SEAL CARRIER INSTALLATION</title>
        <para>Install rear oil seal cover as follows:</para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Place a new gasket into rear oil seal cover (
                <emph type="bold">Figure
                    <hotlnk xrefid="ef1600739">7.39</hotlnk>
                </emph>
                ).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install rear oil seal cover. Secure to crankcase by finger-tightening the mounting bolts.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Rotate/twist cover to align the oil seal cover with crankcase oil pan rail. Use straight
                edge,
                <emph type="bold">OEM1293</emph>to verify (
                <emph type="bold">Figure
                    <hotlnk xrefid="ef1600740">7.40</hotlnk>
                </emph>
                ).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">When the rear cover is aligned, tighten the mounting bolts to the special torque value (
                <emph type="bold">Figure
                    <hotlnk xrefid="ef1600741">7.41</hotlnk>
                </emph>
                ).
            </para>
            <figure id="ef1600739" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="eg6908" filename="../figeg6/EG6908.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 7.39 Rear Oil Seal Carrier Gasket</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">1. Gasket</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <figure id="ef1600740" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="eg6167" filename="../figeg6/EG6167.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 7.40 Aligning Rear Oil Seal Carrier</caption>
            </figure>
            <figure id="ef1600741" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="eg5276" filename="../figeg5/EG5276.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 7.41 Securing Rear Oil Seal Carrier</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
